title: Ep. #129 | Catching Up: Tiger JK
description:
Artist, father, and former Floridian Taekwondo Master, Tiger JK, regales his incredible journey of becoming the person he is today. As one of the main pioneers of South Korea's now budding hip-hop music and culture scene, Tiger JK's pathway to success has not always been clear but seemingly destined all the same.
